The paper deals with video inpainting, which is a computer vision task related to image and video processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel deep network architecture, which involves training a neural network, making it relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of recurrent feedback and temporal memory module, which are related to machine learning and deep learning, respectively, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves generating plausible content, which is related to graphics, making cs.GR (Computer Graphics) another possible category. Finally, the paper involves synthesizing still-unknown regions, which is related to image and video synthesis, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another possible category.
